22:55.332 --> 22:57.457
What do we got here?
(farting)

22:57.540 --> 22:59.332
Look at that,
he's shitting in the hat.

22:59.415 --> 23:02.165
Shit hats for
everybody! Woo!

23:02.248 --> 23:04.373
(crowd cheering)

23:06.457 --> 23:09.499
Mike, Mike. Soledad O'Brien
with Salon.com
Facebook live stream.

23:09.582 --> 23:11.874
You won in the courtroom.
How does it feel?

23:11.957 --> 23:14.165
(laughing) Sorry,
just being hilarious.

23:14.248 --> 23:16.041
Those are my boys over there.

23:16.123 --> 23:19.207
It's a great day for
justice and for people
who love Adam Sandler,

23:19.290 --> 23:22.540
which is, I think, all of us,
so America won today.

23:22.624 --> 23:25.999
And to my opponent, Phil,
I would just like to say...

23:26.082 --> 23:28.707
Suck my (bleeping)

23:28.791 --> 23:29.999
...dick! (laughs)

23:30.082 --> 23:32.290
Send that Carrey
motherfucker to jail!

23:32.373 --> 23:35.457
Lock him up! Lock him up!
Lock him up!

23:35.540 --> 23:36.999
Woo-hoo!

23:37.123 --> 23:39.832
