-Phil: Seven doo-doos...

24:59.624 --> 25:01.290
Both: ...and I can pee-pee.

25:01.373 --> 25:05.957
Seven doo-doos,
and I can pee-pee!

25:06.041 --> 25:08.332
Phil: Yeah!

25:08.415 --> 25:10.999
I can't wait
to be rich!

25:11.082 --> 25:13.082
